title: 2016 CHAN qualifier: Ivory Coast coach Dussuyer points out Ghana's attacking threat
text:
18:55 CET 2016 CHAN qualifier: Ivory Coast coach Dussuyer points out Ghana's attacking threat - www.ghanasoccernet.com Michael Dussuyer 
Ivory Coast coach Michel Dussuyer praised Ghana's attack after the local Elephants conceded late in their 2-1 defeat in their 2016 CHAN qualifier. 
The visitors took the lead through Sangare Ibrahim on 33 minutes before Joel Fameyeh first leveled on 45 minutes and snatched the winner in the 89 th minute. 
For more Ghana football news visit www.ghanasoccernet.com
